resources.description: Through the analysis of the dynamic model of the induction motor, taking characteristics of the c ontrol system, this text puts forward some methods to improve the dynamic performance of as ynchronous servo motors from the angle of motor body design. In SIMULINK environment, an analysis from simple to complex of a model of induction motor is adopted to explore and validate these methods. Finally, specific optimization strategies ar e offered to illustrate the feasibility of these methods.
resources.name: Preliminary Study on Improving the Dynamic Performance of Asynchronous Servo Motors
